# EC2 Lab 2 — Steps

## Step 1: Modify Security Group
- Edited inbound rules
- Set:
  - Type: SSH
  - Port: 22
  - Source: 0.0.0.0/0

## Step 2: Connect via SSH
- Used private key to connect:
  ssh -i key.pem ubuntu@<PUBLIC-IP>

## Step 3: Confirm Exposure
- Instance is reachable from any IP
- No restriction on who can attempt SSH login

## Step 4: Leave Configuration Open (for testing)
- Did not restrict access yet to simulate real risk
